ollywood segment earlier this year, his descent was discreet enough that onlookers did not connect it to the Olympic-themed project.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1028, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999976807885, \"rank\": 2.319392739609521e-09, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sources\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"Cruise\", \"from\": 1010, \"to\": 1016}, {\"ngram\": \"his descent\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"onlookers\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic-themed project\", \"from\": 1134, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the final details of Cruise's Paris stunt are still under wraps, there is a possibility that a stunt double might step in for logistical and safety reasons.\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1325, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1199, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.582162703268963e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final details\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"wraps\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"a possibility\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"a stunt\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"logistical and safety reasons\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Insiders credit Cruise with proposing the idea to the International Olympic Committee, aiming to create a series of stunts to bridge the Paris and Los Angeles games.\", \"from\": 1327, \"to\": 1492, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1381, \"end\": 1412, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.