gram\": \"July\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This marks the third time the city will host the Olympics, having previously done so in 1932 and 1984.\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1828}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise's involvement in Olympic ceremonies is not new.\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cruise's involvement\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic ceremonies\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two decades ago, he participated in the torch relay for the 2004 Athens Olympics, carrying the torch through Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2074, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2062, \"end\": 2073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1971088462683617e-13, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the torch relay\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2004 Athens Olympics\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2033}, {\"ngram\": \"the torch\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2053}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His upcoming performance at the Paris Olympics is yet another testament to his enduring legacy in both the entertainment and sports worlds.\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His upcoming performance\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"another testament\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2146}, {\"ngram\": \"his enduring legacy\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2169}, {\"ngram\": \"both the entertainment and sports worlds\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In some ways, this stunt is n